<p>Alpha Consumer Services is now in co-operation with Norwegian web hosting company Dahlske Bank for the hosting of Alpha Consumer Services web site. All content and customer data has been successfully moved to the new servers and is available through secure login.</p>
<p>Dahlske Bank has a quadruple backup system, continuously backing up any changes to customer data, guaranteeing more than 99.9% uptime and is located in a hidden fallout shelter. Owner and administrator of Dahlske Bank, Daniel Dahl, says that his data loss prevention hardware is unique and exceptional, and adds &#8220;that life on Earth as we know it would end long before any data is lost in our innovative and cutting-edge system&#8221;.</p>
<p>For more information regarding Dahlske Bank, visit their web site at <a href="http://www.dahlskebank.com/" target="_blank">www.dahlskebank.com</a>.</p>
